# 🎨 Chit Chat UI Design Kit

A lightweight, scalable design system for the **Chit Chat** app — built to support consistent UI development with a playful and modern aesthetic.

## 📁 Contents

- **Typography Tokens**
- **Color Tokens**
- **Spacing System**
- **UI Components** (Buttons, Inputs, Tags)
- **Icons & Grids**
- **Component Preview Page**

---

## 🔤 Typography

| Style     | Font           | Size | Weight   | Usage             |
|-----------|----------------|------|----------|-------------------|
| Heading   | Sanitan One    | 48px | Bold     | App titles, hero  |
| Body Text | Sitara         | 16px | Regular  | Paragraphs, UI    |

---

## 🎨 Color Tokens

| Role               | Hex Code |
|--------------------|----------|
| Gradient Start     | `#FF7485`|
| Gradient Middle    | `#F66BC6`|
| Gradient End       | `#CF95DC`|
| Primary Text       | `#252598`|
| Accent             | `#93D7FF`|
| Highlight          | `#ED1ED1`|
| Background         | `#FDFDFD`|

---

## 📏 Spacing Tokens

- **Margin:** 20px  
- **Gutter:** 20px  
- **Grid:** 6 Rows × 6 Columns

---

## 🧩 Components

### 🔘 Buttons
- Default
- Hover
- Disabled

### 🧾 Inputs
- Default field
- Focused field

### 🏷️ Tags
- Tag 1, Tag 2, Tag 3

### 🧭 Icons
- Sizes: 24×, 20×, 16×, 12×, 10×, 8×

---

## 🖼️ Preview Page
Includes a mock layout combining typography, colors, spacing, and components in one unified view.

---

## 📌 Notes
This design kit is structured for handoff-ready use in **Figma**, and can be adapted into front-end frameworks using tokens or variables.

